      "content": "it's just not a \"story\" to me right now. it's just the weight of it all. everything feels so empty and pointless, like no matter what i do or who i am, it's all just going to vanish anyway. why even bother trying to build anything or be anything if the end result is just... silence? it feels more honest to just accept that nothing matters.",
